   Treatment of property owned by partnerships, etc.
   (A)
   In general
   For purposes of this subsection, if—
   (i)
   any property which (but for this subparagraph) is not
   tax-exempt use property
   is owned by a partnership which has both a
   tax-exempt entity
   and a person who is not a
   tax-exempt entity
