   Determination where allocations vary
   For purposes of clause (i), if a
   tax-exempt entity
   ’s share of partnership items of income or gain (excluding gain allocated under
   section 704(c)
   ) may vary during the period such entity is a partner in the partnership, such share shall be the highest share such entity may receive.
