   Computer
   The term “
   computer
   ” means a programmable electronically activated device which—
   (I)
   is capable of accepting information, applying prescribed processes to the information, and supplying the results of these processes with or without human intervention, and
   (II)
   consists of a central processing unit containing extensive storage, logic, arithmetic, and control capabilities.
