   Exceptions
   The term “
   computer or peripheral equipment
   ” shall not include—
   (I)
   any equipment which is an integral part of other property which is not a
   computer
   ,
   (II)
   typewriters, calculators, adding and accounting machines, copiers, duplicating equipment, and similar equipment, and
   (III)
   equipment of a kind used primarily for amusement or entertainment of the user.
